Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's heart is about to open up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't make any mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Yano's heart will open all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understanding the importance of this step forward, we can look even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just keep looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:28.81,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:34.78,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:40.91,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:46.87,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:54.26,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:58.97,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:04.89,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:13.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:18.70,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:25.83,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:32.59,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:28.81,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:34.78,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:40.91,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:46.87,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:54.26,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:58.97,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:04.89,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:13.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:18.70,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:25.83,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:32.59,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:46.60,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1100,900)\fscx113.75\fscy103.75\pos(159,384)}Episode 19 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.55,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You made up with Yano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.56,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say "yeah" like that... did you really think this over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you're not just getting caught in the flow of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just couldn't leave him alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You really did just get caught in the flow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maybe"? Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've decided to start over, I'm going to see it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... if you're that determined, we'll still cheer you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did those two hook up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, any of you guys free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding a hook-up party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some fresh new girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't get enough guys to come. Anyone wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Take?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, don't bother asking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His type never goes to hook-up parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.52,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna meet at the usual place tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll call you when I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if nothing had happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our daily lives have returned to the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's going to come over for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll get Mom pick to up some cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same old peaceful days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to believe that those days will become something incredibly irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you heading out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time will you be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Late. Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no... it can wait for another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going... somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... yeah, just heading out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading for a bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sit next to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably already have the wrong idea since we got on the bus together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know how to make things awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could say the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went well between you and Takahashi, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going on a date today, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you even tell me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to keep your guard up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been like this since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't give me the whole apology routine, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only piss me off more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've given up halfway though the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went and told me I'd regret it, declared war, and put me though hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I tied you up and tore apart any chance I saw you having.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're just gonna bench yourself in the middle of the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight to the bitter end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be the one telling you this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just so you know, I'm not watching out for you or anything, hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.82,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx163.75\fscy190\pos(559,292)\c&HECF2F9&\frz0.408}City Bus
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.53,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx163.75\fscy190\pos(559,294)\c&HECF2F9&\frz0.045}City Bus
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a surprise! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um... I'm just changing buses here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere special...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:40.75,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fscx171.25\fscy253.75\c&HBB7871&\pos(320,-3)}Sign: Hook-up party
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out to a hook-up party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to a hook-up party, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:41.92,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fscx150\fscy205\pos(320,0)\c&HB77796&}Sign: Hook-up party
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:42.54,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fscx150\fscy205\pos(320,0)\c&HB175AA&}Sign: Hook-up party
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, a hook-up party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get going, Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Takeuchi's busy getting to his hook-up party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.01,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HA769BA&\b1\fscx150\fscy205\pos(320,0)}Sign: Hook-up party
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Information travels fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, neither of us are watching out for each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.26,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b1\c&H7155D6&\fscx166.25\fscy255\pos(10,0)}Sign: Hook-up party
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with that hook-up party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you weirdo... getting entangled with him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He's the one who started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like Takeuchi-kun a whole lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Don't say sick stuff like that, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only speaking the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's compare answer #3 and #4.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I go get us something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you're pretty serious today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always screw around, and we never get any studying done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you're acting weird. What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we talk about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to push yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be because I'm actually nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why now, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel like I might screw up by accident and make you angry again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might yell "get out!" or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that I want to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's okay to act stupid like usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're so obedient and quiet like this, it makes me queasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that it might've just been impulsive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I told him that he passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that I've been waiting for that impulse all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with introductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm Emiko! I like going to those stone-slab baths!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.81,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm running to the bathroom for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on your left down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's all this about? Stone-slab baths?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stone-slab baths are in fashion now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bear flipped...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone else who thinks they can flip, feel free to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bear's gym classes are always a little crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drained... and besides, aren't you guys hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any energy left?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, all the girls are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the first challenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never gotten better than a grade of 5 in gym before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always gets so hyped when there's an audience...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any other challengers out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... he's sure standing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the girls are excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take, you're not gonna give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, it's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. After all, you'd look so lame when you screw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't push yourself or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the second challenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about rare! It's Takeuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this kinda unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success! I guess I can handle this much, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty good, too! Takeuchi-kun sure is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can really feel his intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yano's going up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna spin this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he's gonna try to spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "impossible" is not in this man's dictionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really spun! He did a {\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}1{\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}80!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi's going at it, too! Look at those two crazy guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's doing a full 360! Is it gonna be a 540 next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.39,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\b1\fscx160\fscy197.5\pos(326,304)}As to be expected, the teacher eventually stopped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, geez... my hip hurts like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you settled things, so why are you still at each other's throats?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's the one at my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird that he's still at it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's gym class was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez. Why am I grinning so much about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you wonder if there's anything Yano's not good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something he's not good at... Is there anything he's not good at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first entered high school, that's the question I asked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Yano was so scary to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think back on it, it's kind of mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... he really did look like someone who could do anything back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though now I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what Yano's not good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you're uneasy about something, you tend to get even more uneasy about it the more it's brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Yano, who jumps over the vaulting horse so easily, is no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I think of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I find myself loving him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I noticed this before... your lunches are always packed with whole lot of stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's completely different from the lunches my mom makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always just uses last night's leftovers or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as tasty as it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's mom made this flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's not that good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to describe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to how it looks, it's fairly plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have much of a sense for cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she tries her best, so I overlook that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think her omelets are pretty good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, well... they're the only part that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, they really are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that someone can only have one person most important to them at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to say that, then I'm going to try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't give up on me, I'll never give up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been home all weekend, and you've been coming straight home from school lately, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this might or might not be the case, but I guess everything fell though with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? It has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I still call you my little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take advantage of that little runt's mistakes once in a while, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... what's it mean to fight to the bitter end in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it varies depending on the situation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...whether you end up losing or not, doesn't it just mean the other person knows your feelings, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing changes whether you confess or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then it's better to say nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much sugar you coat your words with, they'll still leave a bad aftertaste when everything's said and done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get over it, the people around you will still have to deal with the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone's honest and open like that, he's just being egotistical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting into an illicit relationship with your best friend's girlfriend is wrong to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you and Moto are both in {\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}11{\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}th grade, you're completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you'd lose to him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl told me she'd form bonds, even if there was nothing to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it have been better to cut into his plans and get her before he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I had to tie him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, the world of love is all about being partial and biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as "fair" and "unfair," "dishonorable" and "honorable."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you set him up and break his arm, if you're fighting with all your might for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't that noble, despite what others might think of you afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Noble, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loving someone else's lover, or stealing someone else's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stealing someone else's love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way to allow such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't figure it out, you don't have the right to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I never would've thought you'd be part of the student council, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost in rock-paper-scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you participate last semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They kinda pushed me into doing it again... It's nothing out of the ordinary, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no one's sitting next to me, so why don't you sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've never had a class together, sitting next to each other sorta feels mysterious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading too much into this coincidence would be weird. I'll talk to him normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how'd things go the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the hook-up party?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Okay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you? I'm glad everything worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... sorry for causing you so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the saying, right?\N"Adversity builds character." No pain, no gain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I believe in that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you said, I think I was the one obsessing over Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, Yano had a lot of uneasy feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why it's my turn to give it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are best like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so like yourself. It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano! Let's go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guys. Gotta run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love his smiling face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I want him to keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to make him smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's what keeps me so full of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I said wasn't a lie, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I know that if that smile was for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was really for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't think I could ever be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you prepare for your presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a haircut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know what you're thinking sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got contacts...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not all girls are babes when they get rid of their glasses like in comics...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one way... the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the only way to allow it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take, Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to another hook-up party. You coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't figure it out at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lot of cuties this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said I wasn't going!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it seems like our lives never change, they slowly do...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like how we never notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the changing of the seasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the same goes for our hearts.
