Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:13.27,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A silent rain falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:19.77,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A slightly chilly rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:26.24,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But it continues to fall, without actually hitting me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:34.29,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it's trying to freeze my heart instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:40.75,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always found your gentle back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:49.18,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,on any day, but where do my
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:53.01,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,winding feelings point?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:23:00.23,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:07.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,before you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:14.08,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep on running
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:20.79,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and we seem like we're going to reach, but don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:24.59,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,At that distance away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:37.10,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain will fall again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:43.90,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A slightly lonely rain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:50.36,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will pour all around and spread
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:57.87,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it's meant to soothe my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:24:04.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always looking at your cute back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:12.76,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,but these winding feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:16.60,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,point me in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:23.90,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:31.24,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,at the end of my search?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:37.62,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep on running
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.62,0:24:44.71,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and we seem like we're going to reach, but don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.71,0:24:46.92,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,At that distance away from you.
