Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.73,0:25:07.82,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.82,0:25:09.78,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try going\N out for just a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.78,0:25:12.28,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Take-chan's first girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.28,0:25:14.95,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go out with some\N girl you don't even like!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.95,0:25:17.45,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to\N hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.99,0:25:21.20,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry\N and become an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.20,0:25:23.12,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I can come\N to steal you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.79,0:25:27.13,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,If only... there were\N such a thing as eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.13,0:25:30.09,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,It does exist. I'm sure of it.
